WEBVTT

00:03.337 --> 00:05.005
‐ I want Project Blue Book

00:05.005 --> 00:07.257
to formally close
the Roswell incident.

00:07.257 --> 00:08.842
‐ Run!

00:08.842 --> 00:11.053
‐ You put Blue Book
in that position and they fail,

00:11.053 --> 00:14.181
those guys won't be the only
ones to lose their jobs.

00:14.181 --> 00:15.849
‐ Somebody left us a message.

00:15.849 --> 00:18.227
Tomorrow at 9:00 a. m.,
I will show the world proof

00:18.227 --> 00:20.562
of what really happened
in Roswell, New Mexico.

00:20.562 --> 00:22.356
‐ Yeah,
I'm actually calling to cancel.

00:22.356 --> 00:24.191
I'm out of town
for a couple days.

00:24.191 --> 00:25.609
‐ Don't be gone too long.

00:25.609 --> 00:27.402
I'll miss you.

00:27.402 --> 00:29.696
‐ There were two
separate crash sites.

00:29.696 --> 00:31.365
Recovered its remains

00:31.365 --> 00:33.617
buried under
a big dead tree on my land.

00:35.410 --> 00:36.578
‐ What is that?

00:38.000 --> 00:44.074
Advertise your product or brand here
